719773f-a.title: Manhattan: Forsyth Street - Broome Street
719773f-a.text:
Forsyth Street, west side, north from and including Broome, to Delancey
Streets. Also shown, are Nos. 306-310 Broome Street, at, adjoining and west
of the N.W. corner of Forsyth Street.
July 18, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
